{"_id":"iWsEyuQFwdhxcGZc","name":"Dark Stillness","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Frequency</strong> Once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are suffering from persistent mental damage caused by your ebon evoker adjustments.&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You steady your mind, this counts as having provided particularly effective aid to yourself to end your persistent mental damage. If you are still affected by a spell or condition that could force you to speak, you may attempt to counteract it, using half your level rounded up as your counteract level and your spell attack modifier as your counteract modifier.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-13T18:47:23.148-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UlmlSYUqcCGQIOY3","name":"Ebon Evoker Dedication","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have proven you bear enough resilience and responsibility to carry the onus of your terrible knowledge. You gain access to the Ebon Infusion action and may use it once per day. At 5th level and every 4 levels thereafter you may use Ebon Infusion an additional time per day.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> You can't select another dedication feat before gaining two other feats from this archetype.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["archetype","class","dedication"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-09T19:21:08.522-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Ebon Affect"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UlmlSYUqcCGQIOY3"}}}
{"_id":"SlQMT4UlFqKb8Oxh","name":"Ebon Infusion","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day (see Ebon Evoker Dedication)</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You infuse your spell with the secrets of your ebon knowledge. If the next action you use is to Cast a Spell that deals damage or inflicts a condition, it gains a benefit listed below, if the spell deals damage and inflicts a condition, choose one option when you Cast the Spell.</p>\n<p><strong> Damage</strong> For every die of damage the spell deals in damage it deals an additional point of damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Condition</strong> The condition inflicted has its value increased by 1, if the condition does not have a value, its duration is increased by half (minimum 1 round). If the duration is sustained, the duration extends by half the period the spell remained sustained.&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","metamagic"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-09T19:24:33.883-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"y5waOyasspFcXw4r","name":"Ebon Warp","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have learned to bend spells to your whim. When you cast a spell modified by Ebon Infusion with an area and no duration, you may include an additional number of 5-foot spaces equal to the number of ebon evoker feats you have. These spaces must be contiguous with the original area of the spell. In place of adding a space, you may remove a 5-foot space from the area of the spell, causing any creature within that space that is not within another affected space to not suffer the effects of the spell.&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-13T18:39:06.264-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Ebon Evoker Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6z1qS1tfYrQbClTD","name":"Speak the Words","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You force yourself to speak, unleashing the energies of the secrets you hold deep within you on yourself and others, causing you to take persistent mental damage from your ebon evoker adjustments. Creatures in a 30-foot emanation take persistent force damage equal to the amount of persistent mental damage you suffer from this act @Check[type:fortitude|basic:true|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.spellDC.value)].</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["archetype","auditory","evocation"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-13T19:35:16.661-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Ebon Evoker Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tifNXDs02LQKstfc","name":"Terrifying Veil","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You invoke the dark mystery of your ebon veil targeting foes in a @Template[type:cone|distance:15]. Creatures that gaze into your veil must attempt a Will save against your spell DC. Regardless of the result of their save, targets are immune to your Terrifying Veil for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is&nbsp;@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is&nbsp;@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is&nbsp;@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}&nbsp;and&nbsp;@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 1}&nbsp;by its fear of the unknown.&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["archetype","emotion","enchantment","mental","visual"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.764,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-07-13T18:44:07.679-04:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.12.2.10"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Ebon Evoker Dedication"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wJlZYfbdjdvT8g1Z":3},"flags":{}}
